@page "/performance"

<PageTitle>Performance</PageTitle>

<main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="eyebrow">Performance overview</div>
        <h1>Track live results and <span class="gradient-text">testing data</span></h1>
        <p>Review the Kohinoor EA proof layer through live-result presentation, backtest context, and growth-based performance visibility.</p>
        <div class="notice-box">
          <span class="mini-label">Performance proof</span>
          <p>The layout below organizes verified live records, historical testing context, and growth snapshots in a format buyers can review quickly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="live-results">
      <div class="container performance-proof-grid">
        <article class="performance-proof-card">
          <div class="proof-card-head">
            <span class="badge">Live module</span>
            <strong>Verified account proof</strong>
          </div>
          <h3>Myfxbook / Live Results</h3>
          <p>Use this area for a Myfxbook widget, verified live account link, or broker-connected performance snapshot.</p>
          <div class="proof-visual proof-visual-live">
            <div class="proof-visual-top">
              <span>Live account</span>
              <strong>Ready for embed</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="proof-chart-bars">
              <span style="height: 35%"></span>
              <span style="height: 48%"></span>
              <span style="height: 42%"></span>
              <span style="height: 58%"></span>
              <span style="height: 64%"></span>
              <span style="height: 72%"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="proof-list">
            <li>Best for forward-tested account snapshots</li>
            <li>Show broker, account type, drawdown, and growth</li>
            <li>Add the verified link when your module is ready</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="https://wa.me/919047828806?text=Hi%20I%20want%20to%20view%20verified%20live%20results%20for%20Kohinoor%20EA">Request Live Link</a>
        </article>

        <article class="performance-proof-card featured-proof">
          <div class="proof-card-head">
            <span class="badge">Backtest evidence</span>
            <strong>MT4 strategy report</strong>
          </div>
          <h3>Backtest Report</h3>
          <p>Present historical test reports with dates, modeling quality, spread assumptions, deposit size, and XAUUSD settings.</p>
          <div class="proof-report">
            <div><span>Model</span><strong>MT4</strong></div>
            <div><span>Pair</span><strong>XAUUSD</strong></div>
            <div><span>Data</span><strong>History</strong></div>
            <div><span>Status</span><strong>Working</strong></div>
          </div>
          <ul class="proof-list">
            <li>Upload report image or PDF summary here</li>
            <li>Label every assumption clearly</li>
            <li>Keep historical tests separate from live results</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/contact">Ask for Backtest Report</a>
        </article>

        <article class="performance-proof-card">
          <div class="proof-card-head">
            <span class="badge">Growth snapshot</span>
            <strong>Equity curve view</strong>
          </div>
          <h3>Growth Chart</h3>
          <p>Use this area to show cumulative growth, equity consistency, and drawdown-aware progress over time.</p>
          <div class="proof-visual proof-visual-growth">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 420 180" role="img" aria-label="Sample growth curve">
              <path d="M20 145 C70 130 92 95 132 110 C168 124 184 74 228 82 C270 90 284 48 326 54 C360 60 382 34 404 22" />
              <path class="proof-area" d="M20 145 C70 130 92 95 132 110 C168 124 184 74 228 82 C270 90 284 48 326 54 C360 60 382 34 404 22 L404 160 L20 160 Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <ul class="proof-list">
            <li>Show growth beside drawdown context</li>
            <li>Use monthly snapshots for easier reading</li>
            <li>Link the chart back to verified performance data</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/pricing#plans">View Access Plans</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container panel">
        <h2 class="section-title">Present performance with context</h2>
        <p>Use verified live records and clearly labeled backtest conditions so visitors understand the difference between historical modeling and forward-tested results.</p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="https://wa.me/919047828806?text=Hi%20I%20want%20the%20live%20results%20for%20Kohinoor%20EA">Request Full Details</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/pricing#plans">Secure Your Access</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div><strong>Kohinoor EA</strong></div>
      <div><p>Performance page presenting live records, backtest context, and growth visibility.</p></div>
    </div>
  </footer>


